tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依d飛機新聞我覺得冇單比到人信心 你話美團，騰仔要破產 就唔同講法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"呢d全部係本土內需"},{"pid":"52587fa23330cf0206c3fdffa07a9399843990ce","tid":1970941,"uid":47475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e19738f04ce17208280ba783c554ed84d31180e2","tid":1970941,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"行返希特拉條舊路咪解決問題囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"太睇得起支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}